<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">MURDOCHS TAKE STEP IN SUCCESSION PLANNING <span class="divider">Â |Â </span></span><!-- end .title --> Rupert Murdoch has taken a big step in making succession plans for his media empire, <b><a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-03-26/news-corp-names-lachlan-murdoch-non-executive-chairman.html">appointing his sons Lachlan and James to top roles</a></b>. Lachlan will become nonexecutive chairman of News Corporation and 21st Century Fox, while James will become co-chief operating officer of 21st Century Fox.</p>
